\": \"Less than 24 hours after the shock withdrawal of Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce from the semi-finals of the women's 100m on Saturday's third day, Jamaican fans received another jolt early Sunday morning with the news that Jackson, the back-to-back World Championships gold medallist in the 200m and the fastest woman alive over the distance, had been withdraw.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\"}, {\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999999359438354, \"rank\": 6.405612016260973e-08, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9986054810897186, \"rank\": 0.0012811443099326803, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Jackson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shock withdrawal\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 100m\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday's third day\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"another jolt\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 567}, {\"ngram